_sText: 007_facility_dm This map was originally created by Semedi for Goldeneye Source. All credit goes to him and Rareware for originally designing this level in the first place. This DM Version has: - A Nav File - Spawn Text File - A Radar Map - Cubemaps Put the 007_facility_dm.bsp into cstrike/maps and put 007_facility_dm.txt into cstrike/cfg/cssdm/spawns to install the map. Note: This map was made for Death Match, nothing else. The default CT spawn area doesn't even have a buy zone, because you wouldn't need one in Death Match so don't complain about things like that. If you have any other questions or comments though, please let me know.
